  "events": [ {
    "tStartMs": 33,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Put it inside me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3069,
    "dDurationMs": 1368,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's what Silicon Valley"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 4437,
    "dDurationMs": 3137,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is saying about something called peptides."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7607,
    "dDurationMs": 4605,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "These ostensibly magic drugs\naren't exactly legal and are often sourced"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12212,
    "dDurationMs": 3403,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from unregulated factories in China,\nbut that hasn't stopped them"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15615,
    "dDurationMs": 4605,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from exploding in popularity amongst\nin the know techies and corporate bigwigs"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20353,
    "dDurationMs": 3771,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with promises that they can do things\nlike burn our fat, tan"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 24124,
    "dDurationMs": 5138,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "our skin, focus our brains,\nimprove our sleep, and horny our libidos."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 29295,
    "dDurationMs": 3404,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it's promises like these\nthat are just now inspiring"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 32699,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "normies to start poking themselves\nwith the magic juice."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 36269,
    "dDurationMs": 3504,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yet one question remains:\nwhat even is this stuff?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 40173,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And is this all going to end really bad?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 44310,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Okay, that was two questions, but-"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 51584,
    "dDurationMs": 3103,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Simply put, peptides\nare chains of amino acids"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 54687,
    "dDurationMs": 3771,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that help your body perform\nvarious functions, from healing a muscle"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 58458,
    "dDurationMs": 3704,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "tear, growing skin cells,\nor producing an entire above ground"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 62162,
    "dDurationMs": 3069,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "pool's worth of testosterone,\nas mine's been known to do."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 65265,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There are some famous peptides\nyou've probably heard of, like insulin"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 68268,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and oxytocin."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 69269,
    "dDurationMs": 1401,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Peptides like these are created"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 70670,
    "dDurationMs": 3504,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "inside of the body using proteins\nthat we consume through food."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 74174,
    "dDurationMs": 2369,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But the things that we'll be talking about\ntoday are peptides"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 76543,
    "dDurationMs": 2536,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are created synthetically in a lab\nand are then"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 79079,
    "dDurationMs": 2402,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "injected straight into your body\nwith a needle."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 81481,
    "dDurationMs": 4171,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You might be familiar with glucagon\nlike peptide one or GLP-1."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 85652,
    "dDurationMs": 2035,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Drugs like ozempic or wegovy"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 87687,
    "dDurationMs": 3504,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Inject a version of GLP-1 into your\nbody, which helps you lose weight."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 91224,
    "dDurationMs": 3470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "These shots are legal\nand have quite frankly, been everywhere"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 94694,
    "dDurationMs": 4605,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the last few years, but their popularity\nhas spurred a hunt to find new injectable"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 99299,
    "dDurationMs": 3036,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "peptide drugs that might also yield\nother health benefits,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 102368,
    "dDurationMs": 4605,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is how we've reached the more\ncolloquial umbrella term of peptides,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 106973,
    "dDurationMs": 4671,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "referring to stuff like GLP-1s,\nbut also dozens of different experimental"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 111644,
    "dDurationMs": 1535,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and off-label shots"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 113179,
    "dDurationMs": 3804,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with names that, when spoken, make\nyou sound like a total droid."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 117016,
    "dDurationMs": 5406,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Sorry but I'm not doing these subtitles"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 122422,
    "dDurationMs": 4404,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They're saying insane stuff"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 126826,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Just long strings of letters and numbers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 129963,
    "dDurationMs": 4938,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Still going"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 135368,
    "dDurationMs": 2569,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This guy was particularly enthusiastic"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 137937,
    "dDurationMs": 634,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Still going"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 138571,
    "dDurationMs": 2436,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Still going"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 142675,
    "dDurationMs": 401,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 143076,
    "dDurationMs": 3103,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Since these shots are unregulated\nand understudied,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 146179,
    "dDurationMs": 3837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "not a ton is scientifically known\nabout what peptides will do to your body."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 150016,
    "dDurationMs": 5072,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yet peptide takers hope that stuff\nlike BPC-157 will repair their muscles,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 155221,
    "dDurationMs": 4838,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "GHKCU will reduce their wrinkles, Dihexia will help them focus more,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 160260,
    "dDurationMs": 2802,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Ipamoralin them sleep better,\nand Slytherin"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 163062,
    "dDurationMs": 3304,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "will help them diabolically scheme\nagainst the boy who lived."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 169502,
    "dDurationMs": 2569,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Sometimes\nthese peptides are sold individually,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 172071,
    "dDurationMs": 3737,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but they can also be combined\nto create so-called stacks or"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 175808,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "groups of peptides taken at the same time\nto get different effects."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 179078,
    "dDurationMs": 1569,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Many pep pushers that corner"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 180647,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you in the gym shower\nwill talk about their own unique stack,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 183783,
    "dDurationMs": 3203,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "although certain ones\ncome with fun nicknames like the Wolverine"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 187086,
    "dDurationMs": 1435,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or Glow Stacks."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 188521,
    "dDurationMs": 3837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There's such a broad category of things\nbeing sold as peptides"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 192358,
    "dDurationMs": 1235,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that it's hard to really paint"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 193593,
    "dDurationMs": 3704,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with a broad brush, because on the one\nhand, the GLPs, those are safe."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 197297,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "People have been taking those for,\nyou know, decades now."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 200133,
    "dDurationMs": 1902,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we're currently\nin the early adopter phase,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 202035,
    "dDurationMs": 3703,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just as we've been with any other kind of\nlike new development where there's the,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 205772,
    "dDurationMs": 4504,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, the first crazy guy\nto get a car in the late 19th century."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 210276,
    "dDurationMs": 1302,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And to be clear, like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 211578,
    "dDurationMs": 2235,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there certainly are risks there\nbecause a lot of these things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 213813,
    "dDurationMs": 2603,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "haven't been studied at all, really,\nin a, in a clinical setting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 216416,
    "dDurationMs": 3336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we don't know necessarily\nif the people taking peptides now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 219986,
    "dDurationMs": 2936,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are like the first crazy guy\nto ride a car, as you said,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 222922,
    "dDurationMs": 2770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or like the first guy\nto give their baby opium, essentially."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 227360,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We don't know that, no."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 228528,
    "dDurationMs": 3470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Ezra Marcus is a reporter with glasses\nwho wrote a piece"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 231998,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about his own experience\nuncovering the world of peptides,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 235068,
    "dDurationMs": 3670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "before then deciding\nto put them inside of himself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 238905,
    "dDurationMs": 3937,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I wanted to go through the kind\nof like process that any"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 242842,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "consumer of this stuff would go through,\nso I went through two different routes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 246012,
    "dDurationMs": 5072,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The first was I went to a above board\nregulated to some extent med spa,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 251117,
    "dDurationMs": 3403,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I said, I'm a reporter,\nI'm interested in peptides, like,"
