  }, {
    "tStartMs": 273439,
    "dDurationMs": 1969,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from your kind of teenage looksmaxxers."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 275408,
    "dDurationMs": 3637,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, what I did was\nI went on Reddit, on the Peptides"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 279379,
    "dDurationMs": 3637,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Reddit channel, and I just started DMing\npeople like, hey, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 283016,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I want to talk to you about peptides."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 285018,
    "dDurationMs": 2068,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And some guy was like,\ncool, join my discord."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 287086,
    "dDurationMs": 3404,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there was a representative\nfrom a Chinese factory,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 291257,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "manufacturer in the discord\nwho would sort of handle all their orders"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 294527,
    "dDurationMs": 2136,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and claim to be testing the samples."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 296663,
    "dDurationMs": 3069,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And they and it was all just sort of she\nwas just selling directly to these people."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 299732,
    "dDurationMs": 5806,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I was like, okay, well, I'll just buy\nthe cheapest amount of Retatrutide"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 305538,
    "dDurationMs": 4872,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that they sold, which was ten,\nfive milligram vials for like 150 bucks,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 310543,
    "dDurationMs": 3604,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sent her bitcoin, and two weeks\nlater showed up on my doorstep"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 314147,
    "dDurationMs": 2469,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "labeled, of course, for research purposes\nonly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 316616,
    "dDurationMs": 2269,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Folks, does your investing app\nfeel like a game?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 318885,
    "dDurationMs": 3336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Well, if you're looking for a broker\nthat doesn't also seem like your bookie,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 322255,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I invite you to try out Public."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 324090,
    "dDurationMs": 4238,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Public is the investing platform for folks\nwho take their investing seriously."
