      "utf8": "It's it's not one\nthat you should just do all the time."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 665564,
    "dDurationMs": 3104,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Now, folks, I imagine that\nthe more you hear about peptides"
