      "utf8": "a major part of that future."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 711477,
    "dDurationMs": 4171,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Peptides are going to be,\nI think, a $1 trillion category."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 715681,
    "dDurationMs": 4371,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Injections are now a viable\nform of drug delivery, which opens up"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 720052,
    "dDurationMs": 4938,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the kind of the the the drug purview\nto include other injectable peptides."
