  }, {
    "tStartMs": 725391,
    "dDurationMs": 3770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think over the coming years we're\ngoing to see many GLP-1 like drugs."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 729161,
    "dDurationMs": 3304,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But for everything else to come to market.\nI think many people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 732832,
    "dDurationMs": 3970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "see these broadly\nas these kind of fringe compounds."
