  }, {
    "tStartMs": 738204,
    "dDurationMs": 3937,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "things that are new start kind of fringe\nand then slowly become mainstream, right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 742141,
    "dDurationMs": 1468,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I often recall that"
