    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it would be worth it for what\nit's done for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 977409,
    "dDurationMs": 4371,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Indeed, peptides seem to be a product\nthat speak to our time like no other,"
